metadata.name: Crystalline Architects
metadata.description:

Icy stillness, ISA,
crystalline center point, emergent overlapping dimensions ~

Interwoven with mysterious beings I call ‚Äòplaneswalkers‚Äô,
just for fun,

but the deeper I go into the abyss

to be

without seeking to know,
or to box my experiences into a mental concept

back to stillness

Zero Point,
Shunya
